		<section class="comment-content">
			
			<p>Good information<br />
However, healthy lifestyle is always need not only for our appearance but also for our healthy.<br />
weight loss, not smoking and exercises routine is good instead of taking pills.<br />
noting fast for healthy.<br />
thanks.</p>
		</section>
